sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as WorkspaceCreate
    participant Service as WorkspaceService
    participant FS as Filesystem

    User->>CLI: workspace:create name
    CLI->>Service: create(name)
    Service->>FS: ensure workspaces dir
    Service->>FS: check if workspace exists
    alt already exists
        Service-->>CLI: throw RuntimeException
        CLI-->>User: error output
    else new workspace
        Service->>FS: mkdir workspace path
        Service->>FS: write CLAUDE.md
        Service->>FS: write .code-workspace
        Service-->>CLI: workspace info
        CLI-->>User: success output
    end
